# ---- Build output / artifacts ----
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Oo]ut/
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
x64/
x86/
build/
bld/
artifacts/
*.binlog

# ---- NuGet ----
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
.nuget/
packages/
